                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Why we’ve made this commitment"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-11-23T15:37:06.840-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>We’re committing to a science-based target because our patients expect the best, and they trust us to provide the critical medicines they need when they need them. Climate change is making weather events more frequent and severe, and supply chain disruptions more likely. By taking actions now to lessen its effect, we can ensure our long-term resiliency and sustainability of supporting patients in the long term.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Delivering a science-based target also aligns with our values as a science-based company. Every day we follow where the science leads us. And today the climate science is clear – the ongoing and rapid rise in temperature across our planet will lead to more frequent and severe weather events such as stronger and more intense hurricanes, thunderstorms, heatwaves, wildfires and rising sea levels. Because we believe in science, we believe in doing our part to change this outlook.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2022-11-23T15:07:39.170-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-11-23T15:07:39.170-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-04-22T13:52:02.102-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="The progress we’ve made towards lowering our environmental impact"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-11-23T15:38:34.128-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Our commitment to science-based targets builds on&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/content/dam/abbvie-dotcom/uploads/PDFs/societal-impact/abbvie-esg-action-report.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>the ongoing work we’re doing&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;to reduce our carbon footprint worldwide. Recognizing the environmental risks associated with operating a global business, we've set ambitious, long-term environmental sustainability targets. These include targets for reducing absolute carbon emissions, water and waste generation, achieving zero waste to landfills, and increasing our use of renewable electricity.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
